Type ORM
https://github.com/xeusteerapat/node-typeorm-crud/tree/master/src

Migration: 
https://orkhan.gitbook.io/typeorm/docs/migrations

typeorm migration:create ./src/database/migrations/PostRefactoring
typeorm migration:create ./src/migrations/UserRefactoring

For Run Migration file
-> typeorm -d src/database/app-data-source.ts migration:run
-> typeorm -d src/database/ormconfig.json migration:run
-> typeorm -d ormconfig.json migration:run
-> npm run typeorm migration:run -- -d src/database/app-data-source.ts 

-> typeorm migration:run
-> npx typeorm-ts-node-esm migration:run
-> npx typeorm-ts-node-esm migration:generate ./src/migrations/update-post-table -d ./src/data-source.ts
-> typeorm migration:revert


Entity. 
typeorm entity:create -n User
typeorm entity:create -n Post
typeorm entity:create -n Post -d src/entity


